{"sn12.44:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 12.44 ","sn12.44:0.2":"5. Gahapativagga ","sn12.44:0.3":"Lokasutta ","sn12.44:1.1":"Savatthiyam viharati. ","sn12.44:1.2":"“Lokassa, bhikkhave, samudayanca atthangamanca desessami. ","sn12.44:1.3":"Tam sunatha, sadhukam manasi karotha, bhasissami”ti. ","sn12.44:1.4":"“Evam, bhante”ti kho te bhikkhu bhagavato paccassosum. ","sn12.44:1.5":"Bhagava etadavoca: ","sn12.44:2.1":"“Katamo ca, bhikkhave, lokassa samudayo? ","sn12.44:2.2":"Cakkhunca paticca rupe ca uppajjati cakkhuvinnanam. Tinnam sangati phasso. ","sn12.44:2.3":"Phassapaccaya vedana; ","sn12.44:2.4":"vedanapaccaya tanha; ","sn12.44:2.5":"tanhapaccaya upadanam; ","sn12.44:2.6":"upadanapaccaya bhavo; ","sn12.44:2.7":"bhavapaccaya jati; ","sn12.44:2.8":"jatipaccaya jaramaranam sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupayasa sambhavanti. ","sn12.44:2.9":"Ayam kho, bhikkhave, lokassa samudayo. ","sn12.44:3.1":"Sotanca paticca sadde ca …pe… ","sn12.44:3.2":"ghananca paticca gandhe ca … ","sn12.44:3.3":"jivhanca paticca rase ca … ","sn12.44:3.4":"kayanca paticca photthabbe ca … ","sn12.44:3.5":"mananca paticca dhamme ca uppajjati manovinnanam. Tinnam sangati phasso. ","sn12.44:3.6":"Phassapaccaya vedana …pe… ","sn12.44:3.7":"jatipaccaya jaramaranam sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupayasa sambhavanti. ","sn12.44:3.8":"Ayam kho, bhikkhave, lokassa samudayo. ","sn12.44:4.1":"Katamo ca, bhikkhave, lokassa atthangamo? ","sn12.44:4.2":"Cakkhunca paticca rupe ca uppajjati cakkhuvinnanam. Tinnam sangati phasso. ","sn12.44:4.3":"Phassapaccaya vedana; ","sn12.44:4.4":"vedanapaccaya tanha. ","sn12.44:4.5":"Tassayeva tanhaya asesaviraganirodha upadananirodho; ","sn12.44:4.6":"upadananirodha bhavanirodho …pe… ","sn12.44:4.7":"evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hoti. ","sn12.44:4.8":"Ayam kho, bhikkhave, lokassa atthangamo. ","sn12.44:5.1":"Sotanca paticca sadde ca …pe… ","sn12.44:5.2":"ghananca paticca gandhe ca … ","sn12.44:5.3":"jivhanca paticca rase ca … ","sn12.44:5.4":"kayanca paticca photthabbe ca … ","sn12.44:5.5":"mananca paticca dhamme ca uppajjati manovinnanam. Tinnam sangati phasso. ","sn12.44:5.6":"Phassapaccaya vedana; ","sn12.44:5.7":"vedanapaccaya tanha. ","sn12.44:5.8":"Tassayeva tanhaya asesaviraganirodha upadananirodho; ","sn12.44:5.9":"upadananirodha bhavanirodho …pe… ","sn12.44:5.10":"evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hoti. ","sn12.44:5.11":"Ayam kho, bhikkhave, lokassa atthangamo”ti. ","sn12.44:5.12":"Catuttham. "}